Tuna Stuffed Bell Peppers

45 min
$12.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

FishDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow CarbGluten-Free

Description

Delicious bell peppers filled with a savory tuna mixture, perfect for a healthy meal!

Ingredients

  • bell peppers: 4
  • canned tuna: 2 cans (5 oz each)
  • cooked rice: 1 cup
  • corn: 1 cup
  • shredded cheese: 1 cup
  • plain greek yogurt: 1/2 cup
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
